<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa009001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem, pro occultis filii. Psalmus David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa009002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Confitebor tibi, Domine, in toto corde meo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> narrabo omnia mirabilia tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009003vul">3</span>&nbsp;L&aelig;tabor et exsultabo in te;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> psallam nomini tuo, Altissime.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009004vul">4</span>&nbsp;In convertendo inimicum meum retrorsum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> infirmabuntur, et peribunt a facie tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Quoniam fecisti judicium meum et causam meam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sedisti super thronum, qui judicas justitiam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Increpasti gentes, et periit impius:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nomen eorum delesti in &aelig;ternum, et in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Inimici defecerunt frame&aelig; in finem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et civitates eorum destruxisti.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Periit memoria eorum cum sonitu;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009008vul">8</span>&nbsp;et Dominus in &aelig;ternum permanet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Paravit in judicio thronum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009009vul">9</span>&nbsp;et ipse judicabit orbem terr&aelig; in &aelig;quitate:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> judicabit populos in justitia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Et factus est Dominus refugium pauperi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> adjutor in opportunitatibus, in tribulatione.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Et sperent in te qui noverunt nomen tuum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam non dereliquisti qu&aelig;rentes te, Domine.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Psallite Domino qui habitat in Sion;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> annuntiate inter gentes studia ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009013vul">13</span>&nbsp;quoniam requirens sanguinem eorum recordatus est;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non est oblitus clamorem pauperum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Miserere mei, Domine:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vide humilitatem meam de inimicis meis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009015vul">15</span>&nbsp;qui exaltas me de portis mortis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut annuntiem omnes laudationes tuas in portis fili&aelig; Sion:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009016vul">16</span>&nbsp;exultabo in salutari tuo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Infix&aelig; sunt gentes in interitu quem fecerunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in laqueo isto quem absconderunt</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> comprehensus est pes eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Cognoscetur Dominus judicia faciens;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in operibus manuum suarum comprehensus est peccator.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Convertantur peccatores in infernum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> omnes gentes qu&aelig; obliviscuntur Deum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Quoniam non in finem oblivio erit pauperis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> patientia pauperum non peribit in finem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Exsurge, Domine; non confortetur homo:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> judicentur gentes in conspectu tuo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Constitue, Domine, legislatorem super eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut sciant gentes quoniam homines sunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Ut quid, Domine, recessisti longe;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> despicis in opportunitatibus, in tribulatione?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Dum superbit impius, incenditur pauper:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> comprehenduntur in consiliis quibus cogitant.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Quoniam laudatur peccator in desideriis anim&aelig; su&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et iniquus benedicitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Exacerbavit Dominum peccator:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> secundum multitudinem ir&aelig; su&aelig;, non qu&aelig;ret.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Non est Deus in conspectu ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> inquinat&aelig; sunt vi&aelig; illius in omni tempore.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Auferuntur judicia tua a facie ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> omnium inimicorum suorum dominabitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Dixit enim in corde suo: Non movebor</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a generatione in generationem, sine malo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Cujus maledictione os plenum est, et amaritudine, et dolo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sub lingua ejus labor et dolor.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Sedet in insidiis cum divitibus in occultis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut interficiat innocentem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Oculi ejus in pauperem respiciunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> insidiatur in abscondito, quasi leo in spelunca sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Insidiatur ut rapiat pauperem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> rapere pauperem dum attrahit eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009031vul">31</span>&nbsp;In laqueo suo humiliabit eum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> inclinabit se, et cadet cum dominatus fuerit pauperum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Dixit enim in corde suo: Oblitus est Deus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> avertit faciem suam, ne videat in finem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Exsurge, Domine Deus, exaltetur manus tua;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ne obliviscaris pauperum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Propter quid irritavit impius Deum?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> dixit enim in corde suo: Non requiret.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Vides, quoniam tu laborem et dolorem consideras,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut tradas eos in manus tuas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Tibi derelictus est pauper;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> orphano tu eris adjutor.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009036vul">36</span>&nbsp;Contere brachium peccatoris et maligni;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qu&aelig;retur peccatum illius, et non invenietur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009037vul">37</span>&nbsp;Dominus regnabit in &aelig;ternum, et in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> peribitis, gentes, de terra illius.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009038vul">38</span>&nbsp;Desiderium pauperum exaudivit Dominus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> pr&aelig;parationem cordis eorum audivit auris tua:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa009039vul">39</span>&nbsp;judicare pupillo et humili,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut non apponat ultra magnificare se homo super terram.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
