<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa016001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Oratio David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Exaudi, Domine, justitiam meam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> intende deprecationem meam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Auribus percipe orationem meam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non in labiis dolosis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016002vul">2</span>&nbsp;De vultu tuo judicium meum prodeat;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> oculi tui videant &aelig;quitates.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Probasti cor meum, et visitasti nocte;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> igne me examinasti, et non est inventa in me iniquitas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Ut non loquatur os meum opera hominum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> propter verba labiorum tuorum, ego custodivi vias duras.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Perfice gressus meos in semitis tuis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut non moveantur vestigia mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Ego clamavi, quoniam exaudisti me, Deus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> inclina aurem tuam mihi, et exaudi verba mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Mirifica misericordias tuas,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui salvos facis sperantes in te.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016008vul">8</span>&nbsp;A resistentibus dexter&aelig; tu&aelig; custodi me</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut pupillam oculi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Sub umbra alarum tuarum protege me</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016009vul">9</span>&nbsp;a facie impiorum qui me afflixerunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Inimici mei animam meam circumdederunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016010vul">10</span>&nbsp;adipem suum concluserunt:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> os eorum locutum est superbiam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Projicientes me nunc circumdederunt me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> oculos suos statuerunt declinare in terram.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Susceperunt me sicut leo paratus ad pr&aelig;dam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sicut catulus leonis habitans in abditis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Exsurge, Domine: pr&aelig;veni eum, et supplanta eum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> eripe animam meam ab impio;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> frameam tuam</span>
<span class="poe003"><span class="verse" id="psa016014vul">14</span>&nbsp;ab inimicis manus tu&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Domine, a paucis de terra divide eos in vita eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de absconditis tuis adimpletus est venter eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Saturati sunt filiis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dimiserunt reliquias suas parvulis suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa016015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Ego autem in justitia apparebo conspectui tuo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> satiabor cum apparuerit gloria tua.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
