<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa021001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem, pro susceptione matutina. Psalmus David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa021002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Deus, Deus meus, respice in me: quare me dereliquisti?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> longe a salute mea verba delictorum meorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Deus meus, clamabo per diem, et non exaudies;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et nocte, et non ad insipientiam mihi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Tu autem in sancto habitas, laus Isra&euml;l.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021005vul">5</span>&nbsp;In te speraverunt patres nostri;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> speraverunt, et liberasti eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Ad te clamaverunt, et salvi facti sunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in te speraverunt, et non sunt confusi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Ego autem sum vermis, et non homo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> opprobrium hominum, et abjectio plebis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Omnes videntes me deriserunt me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> locuti sunt labiis, et moverunt caput.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Speravit in Domino, eripiat eum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> salvum faciat eum, quoniam vult eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Quoniam tu es qui extraxisti me de ventre,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> spes mea ab uberibus matris me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021011vul">11</span>&nbsp;In te projectus sum ex utero;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de ventre matris me&aelig; Deus meus es tu:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021012vul">12</span>&nbsp;ne discesseris a me,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam tribulatio proxima est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam non est qui adjuvet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Circumdederunt me vituli multi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tauri pingues obsederunt me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Aperuerunt super me os suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sicut leo rapiens et rugiens.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Sicut aqua effusus sum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dispersa sunt omnia ossa mea:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> factum est cor meum tamquam cera liquescens in medio ventris mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Aruit tamquam testa virtus mea,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et lingua mea adh&aelig;sit faucibus meis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in pulverem mortis deduxisti me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Quoniam circumdederunt me canes multi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> concilium malignantium obsedit me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Foderunt manus meas et pedes meos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021018vul">18</span>&nbsp;dinumeraverunt omnia ossa mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Ipsi vero consideraverunt et inspexerunt me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Diviserunt sibi vestimenta mea,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et super vestem meam miserunt sortem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Tu autem, Domine, ne elongaveris auxilium tuum a me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ad defensionem meam conspice.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Erue a framea, Deus, animam meam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de manu canis unicam meam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Salva me ex ore leonis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et a cornibus unicornium humilitatem meam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Narrabo nomen tuum fratribus meis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in medio ecclesi&aelig; laudabo te.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Qui timetis Dominum, laudate eum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> universum semen Jacob, glorificate eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Timeat eum omne semen Isra&euml;l,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam non sprevit, neque despexit deprecationem pauperis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec avertit faciem suam a me:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cum clamarem ad eum, exaudivit me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Apud te laus mea in ecclesia magna;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vota mea reddam in conspectu timentium eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Edent pauperes, et saturabuntur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et laudabunt Dominum qui requirunt eum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vivent corda eorum in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Reminiscentur et convertentur ad Dominum universi fines terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et adorabunt in conspectu ejus univers&aelig; famili&aelig; gentium:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021029vul">29</span>&nbsp;quoniam Domini est regnum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ipse dominabitur gentium.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Manducaverunt et adoraverunt omnes pingues terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in conspectu ejus cadent omnes qui descendunt in terram.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Et anima mea illi vivet;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et semen meum serviet ipsi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa021032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Annuntiabitur Domino generatio ventura;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et annuntiabunt c&aelig;li justitiam ejus</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> populo qui nascetur, quem fecit Dominus.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
