<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa025001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem. Psalmus David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Judica me, Domine, quoniam ego in innocentia mea ingressus sum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in Domino sperans non infirmabor.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Proba me, Domine, et tenta me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ure renes meos et cor meum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Quoniam misericordia tua ante oculos meos est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et complacui in veritate tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Non sedi cum concilio vanitatis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cum iniqua gerentibus non introibo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Odivi ecclesiam malignantium,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cum impiis non sedebo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Lavabo inter innocentes manus meas,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et circumdabo altare tuum, Domine:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025007vul">7</span>&nbsp;ut audiam vocem laudis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et enarrem universa mirabilia tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Domine, dilexi decorem domus tu&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et locum habitationis glori&aelig; tu&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Ne perdas cum impiis, Deus, animam meam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cum viris sanguinum vitam meam:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025010vul">10</span>&nbsp;in quorum manibus iniquitates sunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> dextera eorum repleta est muneribus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Ego autem in innocentia mea ingressus sum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> redime me, et miserere mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa025012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Pes meus stetit in directo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in ecclesiis benedicam te, Domine.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
