<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa028001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Psalmus David, in consummatione tabernaculi.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Afferte Domino, filii Dei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> afferte Domino filios arietum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Afferte Domino gloriam et honorem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> afferte Domino gloriam nomini ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> adorate Dominum in atrio sancto ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Vox Domini super aquas;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus majestatis intonuit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dominus super aquas multas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Vox Domini in virtute;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vox Domini in magnificentia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Vox Domini confringentis cedros,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et confringet Dominus cedros Libani:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028006vul">6</span>&nbsp;et comminuet eas, tamquam vitulum Libani,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dilectus quemadmodum filius unicornium.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Vox Domini intercidentis flammam ignis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028008vul">8</span>&nbsp;vox Domini concutientis desertum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et commovebit Dominus desertum Cades.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Vox Domini pr&aelig;parantis cervos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et revelabit condensa,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in templo ejus omnes dicent gloriam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Dominus diluvium inhabitare facit,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sedebit Dominus rex in &aelig;ternum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa028011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Dominus virtutem populo suo dabit;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dominus benedicet populo suo in pace.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
