<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa035001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem. Servo Domini ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa035002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Dixit injustus ut delinquat in semetipso:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non est timor Dei ante oculos ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Quoniam dolose egit in conspectu ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut inveniatur iniquitas ejus ad odium.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Verba oris ejus iniquitas, et dolus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> noluit intelligere ut bene ageret.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Iniquitatem meditatus est in cubili suo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> astitit omni vi&aelig; non bon&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> malitiam autem non odivit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Domine, in c&aelig;lo misericordia tua,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et veritas tua usque ad nubes.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Justitia tua sicut montes Dei;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> judicia tua abyssus multa.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Homines et jumenta salvabis, Domine,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035008vul">8</span>&nbsp;quemadmodum multiplicasti misericordiam tuam, Deus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Filii autem hominum in tegmine alarum tuarum sperabunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Inebriabuntur ab ubertate domus tu&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et torrente voluptatis tu&aelig; potabis eos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035010vul">10</span>&nbsp;quoniam apud te est fons vit&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in lumine tuo videbimus lumen.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Pr&aelig;tende misericordiam tuam scientibus te,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et justitiam tuam his qui recto sunt corde.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Non veniat mihi pes superbi&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et manus peccatoris non moveat me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa035013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Ibi ceciderunt qui operantur iniquitatem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> expulsi sunt, nec potuerunt stare.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
