<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa036001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Psalmus ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Noli &aelig;mulari in malignantibus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> neque zelaveris facientes iniquitatem:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036002vul">2</span>&nbsp;quoniam tamquam f&oelig;num velociter arescent,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et quemadmodum olera herbarum cito decident.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Spera in Domino, et fac bonitatem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inhabita terram, et pasceris in divitiis ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Delectare in Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dabit tibi petitiones cordis tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Revela Domino viam tuam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et spera in eo, et ipse faciet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Et educet quasi lumen justitiam tuam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et judicium tuum tamquam meridiem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Subditus esto Domino, et ora eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Noli &aelig;mulari in eo qui prosperatur in via sua;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in homine faciente injustitias.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Desine ab ira, et derelinque furorem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> noli &aelig;mulari ut maligneris.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Quoniam qui malignantur exterminabuntur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sustinentes autem Dominum, ipsi h&aelig;reditabunt terram.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Et adhuc pusillum, et non erit peccator;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qu&aelig;res locum ejus, et non invenies.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Mansueti autem h&aelig;reditabunt terram,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et delectabuntur in multitudine pacis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Observabit peccator justum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et stridebit super eum dentibus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Dominus autem irridebit eum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam prospicit quod veniet dies ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Gladium evaginaverunt peccatores;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> intenderunt arcum suum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut dejiciant pauperem et inopem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut trucident rectos corde.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Gladius eorum intret in corda ipsorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et arcus eorum confringatur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Melius est modicum justo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> super divitias peccatorum multas:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036017vul">17</span>&nbsp;quoniam brachia peccatorum conterentur:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> confirmat autem justos Dominus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Novit Dominus dies immaculatorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et h&aelig;reditas eorum in &aelig;ternum erit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Non confundentur in tempore malo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in diebus famis saturabuntur:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036020vul">20</span>&nbsp;quia peccatores peribunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Inimici vero Domini mox ut honorificati fuerint et exaltati,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> deficientes quemadmodum fumus deficient.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Mutuabitur peccator, et non solvet;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> justus autem miseretur et tribuet:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036022vul">22</span>&nbsp;quia benedicentes ei h&aelig;reditabunt terram;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> maledicentes autem ei disperibunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Apud Dominum gressus hominis dirigentur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et viam ejus volet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Cum ceciderit, non collidetur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia Dominus supponit manum suam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Junior fui, etenim senui;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non vidi justum derelictum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec semen ejus qu&aelig;rens panem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Tota die miseretur et commodat;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et semen illius in benedictione erit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Declina a malo, et fac bonum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inhabita in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036028vul">28</span>&nbsp;quia Dominus amat judicium,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non derelinquet sanctos suos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in &aelig;ternum conservabuntur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Injusti punientur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et semen impiorum peribit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Justi autem h&aelig;reditabunt terram,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inhabitabunt in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi super eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Os justi meditabitur sapientiam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et lingua ejus loquetur judicium.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Lex Dei ejus in corde ipsius,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non supplantabuntur gressus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Considerat peccator justum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qu&aelig;rit mortificare eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Dominus autem non derelinquet eum in manibus ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec damnabit eum cum judicabitur illi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Exspecta Dominum, et custodi viam ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exaltabit te ut h&aelig;reditate capias terram:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cum perierint peccatores, videbis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Vidi impium superexaltatum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et elevatum sicut cedros Libani:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036036vul">36</span>&nbsp;et transivi, et ecce non erat;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qu&aelig;sivi eum, et non est inventus locus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036037vul">37</span>&nbsp;Custodi innocentiam, et vide &aelig;quitatem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam sunt reliqui&aelig; homini pacifico.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036038vul">38</span>&nbsp;Injusti autem disperibunt simul;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> reliqui&aelig; impiorum interibunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036039vul">39</span>&nbsp;Salus autem justorum a Domino;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et protector eorum in tempore tribulationis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa036040vul">40</span>&nbsp;Et adjuvabit eos Dominus, et liberabit eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et eruet eos a peccatoribus, et salvabit eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia speraverunt in eo.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
