<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa038001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem, ipsi Idithun. Canticum David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa038002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Dixi: Custodiam vias meas:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut non delinquam in lingua mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Posui ori meo custodiam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cum consisteret peccator adversum me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Obmutui, et humiliatus sum, et silui a bonis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dolor meus renovatus est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Concaluit cor meum intra me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in meditatione mea exardescet ignis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Locutus sum in lingua mea:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Notum fac mihi, Domine, finem meum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et numerum dierum meorum quis est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut sciam quid desit mihi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Ecce mensurabiles posuisti dies meos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et substantia mea tamquam nihilum ante te.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Verumtamen universa vanitas, omnis homo vivens.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Verumtamen in imagine pertransit homo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sed et frustra conturbatur:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> thesaurizat, et ignorat cui congregabit ea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Et nunc qu&aelig; est exspectatio mea: nonne Dominus?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et substantia mea apud te est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Ab omnibus iniquitatibus meis erue me:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> opprobrium insipienti dedisti me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Obmutui, et non aperui os meum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam tu fecisti;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038011vul">11</span>&nbsp;amove a me plagas tuas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038012vul">12</span>&nbsp;A fortitudine manus tu&aelig; ego defeci in increpationibus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> propter iniquitatem corripuisti hominem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et tabescere fecisti sicut araneam animam ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> verumtamen vane conturbatur omnis homo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Exaudi orationem meam, Domine, et deprecationem meam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> auribus percipe lacrimas meas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Ne sileas, quoniam advena ego sum apud te,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et peregrinus sicut omnes patres mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa038014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Remitte mihi, ut refrigerer</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> priusquam abeam et amplius non ero.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
