<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa047001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Psalmus cantici. Filiis Core, secunda sabbati.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa047002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Magnus Dominus et laudabilis nimis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in civitate Dei nostri, in monte sancto ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Fundatur exsultatione univers&aelig; terr&aelig; mons Sion;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> latera aquilonis, civitas regis magni.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Deus in domibus ejus cognoscetur</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cum suscipiet eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Quoniam ecce reges terr&aelig; congregati sunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> convenerunt in unum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Ipsi videntes, sic admirati sunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> conturbati sunt, commoti sunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Tremor apprehendit eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ibi dolores ut parturientis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047008vul">8</span>&nbsp;in spiritu vehementi conteres naves Tharsis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Sicut audivimus, sic vidimus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in civitate Domini virtutum, in civitate Dei nostri:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus fundavit eam in &aelig;ternum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Suscepimus, Deus, misericordiam tuam</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in medio templi tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Secundum nomen tuum, Deus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sic et laus tua in fines terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> justitia plena est dextera tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047012vul">12</span>&nbsp;L&aelig;tetur mons Sion,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exsultent fili&aelig; Jud&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> propter judicia tua, Domine.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Circumdate Sion, et complectimini eam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> narrate in turribus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Ponite corda vestra in virtute ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et distribuite domos ejus, ut enarretis in progenie altera.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa047015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Quoniam hic est Deus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus noster in &aelig;ternum, et in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ipse reget nos in s&aelig;cula.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
