<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa049001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Psalmus Asaph.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Deus deorum Dominus locutus est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et vocavit terram a solis ortu usque ad occasum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Ex Sion species decoris ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Deus manifeste veniet;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus noster, et non silebit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Ignis in conspectu ejus exardescet;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in circuitu ejus tempestas valida.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Advocabit c&aelig;lum desursum, et terram,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> discernere populum suum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Congregate illi sanctos ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui ordinant testamentum ejus super sacrificia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Et annuntiabunt c&aelig;li justitiam ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam Deus judex est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Audi, populus meus, et loquar;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Isra&euml;l, et testificabor tibi:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus, Deus tuus ego sum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Non in sacrificiis tuis arguam te;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> holocausta autem tua in conspectu meo sunt semper.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Non accipiam de domo tua vitulos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> neque de gregibus tuis hircos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049010vul">10</span>&nbsp;quoniam me&aelig; sunt omnes fer&aelig; silvarum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> jumenta in montibus, et boves.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Cognovi omnia volatilia c&aelig;li,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et pulchritudo agri mecum est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Si esuriero, non dicam tibi:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> meus est enim orbis terr&aelig; et plenitudo ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Numquid manducabo carnes taurorum?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> aut sanguinem hircorum potabo?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Immola Deo sacrificium laudis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et redde Altissimo vota tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Et invoca me in die tribulationis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> eruam te, et honorificabis me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Peccatori autem dixit Deus: Quare tu enarras justitias meas?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et assumis testamentum meum per os tuum?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Tu vero odisti disciplinam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et projecisti sermones meos retrorsum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Si videbas furem, currebas cum eo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cum adulteris portionem tuam ponebas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Os tuum abundavit malitia,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et lingua tua concinnabat dolos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Sedens adversus fratrem tuum loquebaris,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et adversus filium matris tu&aelig; ponebas scandalum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049021vul">21</span>&nbsp;H&aelig;c fecisti, et tacui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Existimasti inique quod ero tui similis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> arguam te, et statuam contra faciem tuam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Intelligite h&aelig;c, qui obliviscimini Deum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nequando rapiat, et non sit qui eripiat.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa049023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Sacrificium laudis honorificabit me,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et illic iter quo ostendam illi salutare Dei.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
