<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa058001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem, ne disperdas. David in tituli inscriptionem, quando misit Saul et custodivit domum ejus ut eum interficeret.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa058002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Eripe me de inimicis meis, Deus meus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ab insurgentibus in me libera me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Eripe me de operantibus iniquitatem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de viris sanguinum salva me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Quia ecce ceperunt animam meam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> irruerunt in me fortes.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Neque iniquitas mea, neque peccatum meum, Domine;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sine iniquitate cucurri, et direxi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Exsurge in occursum meum, et vide:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tu, Domine Deus virtutum, Deus Isra&euml;l,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> intende ad visitandas omnes gentes:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non miserearis omnibus qui operantur iniquitatem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Convertentur ad vesperam, et famem patientur ut canes:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et circuibunt civitatem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Ecce loquentur in ore suo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et gladius in labiis eorum: quoniam quis audivit?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Et tu, Domine, deridebis eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ad nihilum deduces omnes gentes.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Fortitudinem meam ad te custodiam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia, Deus, susceptor meus es:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Deus meus misericordia ejus pr&aelig;veniet me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Deus ostendet mihi super inimicos meos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ne occidas eos, nequando obliviscantur populi mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Disperge illos in virtute tua,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et depone eos, protector meus, Domine:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058013vul">13</span>&nbsp;delictum oris eorum, sermonem labiorum ipsorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et comprehendantur in superbia sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et de execratione et mendacio annuntiabuntur</span>
<span class="poe003"><span class="verse" id="psa058014vul">14</span>&nbsp;in consummatione:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in ira consummationis, et non erunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et scient quia Deus dominabitur Jacob, et finium terr&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Convertentur ad vesperam, et famem patientur ut canes:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et circuibunt civitatem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Ipsi dispergentur ad manducandum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> si vero non fuerint saturati, et murmurabunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Ego autem cantabo fortitudinem tuam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exsultabo mane misericordiam tuam:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia factus es susceptor meus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et refugium meum in die tribulationis me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa058018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Adjutor meus, tibi psallam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia Deus susceptor meus es;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus meus, misericordia mea.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
