<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa065001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem. Canticum psalmi resurrectionis.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Jubilate Deo, omnis terra;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065002vul">2</span>&nbsp;psalmum dicite nomini ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> date gloriam laudi ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Dicite Deo: Quam terribilia sunt opera tua, Domine!</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in multitudine virtutis tu&aelig; mentientur tibi inimici tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Omnis terra adoret te, et psallat tibi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> psalmum dicat nomini tuo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Venite, et videte opera Dei:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> terribilis in consiliis super filios hominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Qui convertit mare in aridam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in flumine pertransibunt pede:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ibi l&aelig;tabimur in ipso.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Qui dominatur in virtute sua in &aelig;ternum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> oculi ejus super gentes respiciunt:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui exasperant non exaltentur in semetipsis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Benedicite, gentes, Deum nostrum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et auditam facite vocem laudis ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065009vul">9</span>&nbsp;qui posuit animam meam ad vitam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non dedit in commotionem pedes meos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Quoniam probasti nos, Deus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> igne nos examinasti, sicut examinatur argentum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Induxisti nos in laqueum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> posuisti tribulationes in dorso nostro;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065012vul">12</span>&nbsp;imposuisti homines super capita nostra.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Transivimus per ignem et aquam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et eduxisti nos in refrigerium.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Introibo in domum tuam in holocaustis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> reddam tibi vota mea</span>
<span class="poe003"><span class="verse" id="psa065014vul">14</span>&nbsp;qu&aelig; distinxerunt labia mea:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et locutum est os meum in tribulatione mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Holocausta medullata offeram tibi, cum incenso arietum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> offeram tibi boves cum hircis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Venite, audite, et narrabo, omnes qui timetis Deum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quanta fecit anim&aelig; me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Ad ipsum ore meo clamavi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exaltavi sub lingua mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Iniquitatem si aspexi in corde meo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non exaudiet Dominus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Propterea exaudivit Deus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et attendit voci deprecationis me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa065020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Benedictus Deus, qui non amovit orationem meam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et misericordiam suam a me.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
