<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa067001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem. Psalmus cantici ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa067002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Exsurgat Deus, et dissipentur inimici ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et fugiant qui oderunt eum a facie ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Sicut deficit fumus, deficiant;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sicut fluit cera a facie ignis, sic pereant peccatores a facie Dei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Et justi epulentur, et exsultent in conspectu Dei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et delectentur in l&aelig;titia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Cantate Deo; psalmum dicite nomini ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> iter facite ei qui ascendit super occasum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dominus nomen illi; exsultate in conspectu ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Turbabuntur a facie ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067006vul">6</span>&nbsp;patris orphanorum, et judicis viduarum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus in loco sancto suo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Deus qui inhabitare facit unius moris in domo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui educit vinctos in fortitudine,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> similiter eos qui exasperant, qui habitant in sepulchris.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Deus, cum egredereris in conspectu populi tui,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cum pertransires in deserto,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067009vul">9</span>&nbsp;terra mota est, etenim c&aelig;li distillaverunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a facie Dei Sinai, a facie Dei Isra&euml;l.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Pluviam voluntariam segregabis, Deus, h&aelig;reditati tu&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et infirmata est, tu vero perfecisti eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Animalia tua habitabunt in ea;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> parasti in dulcedine tua pauperi, Deus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Dominus dabit verbum evangelizantibus, virtute multa.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Rex virtutum dilecti, dilecti;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et speciei domus dividere spolia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Si dormiatis inter medios cleros,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> penn&aelig; columb&aelig; deargentat&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et posteriora dorsi ejus in pallore auri.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Dum discernit c&aelig;lestis reges super eam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nive dealbabuntur in Selmon.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Mons Dei, mons pinguis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> mons coagulatus, mons pinguis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Ut quid suspicamini, montes coagulatos?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> mons in quo beneplacitum est Deo habitare in eo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> etenim Dominus habitabit in finem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Currus Dei decem millibus multiplex, millia l&aelig;tantium;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dominus in eis in Sina, in sancto.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Ascendisti in altum, cepisti captivitatem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> accepisti dona in hominibus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> etenim non credentes inhabitare Dominum Deum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Benedictus Dominus die quotidie:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> prosperum iter faciet nobis Deus salutarium nostrorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Deus noster, Deus salvos faciendi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Domini, Domini exitus mortis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Verumtamen Deus confringet capita inimicorum suorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> verticem capilli perambulantium in delictis suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Dixit Dominus: Ex Basan convertam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> convertam in profundum maris:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067024vul">24</span>&nbsp;ut intingatur pes tuus in sanguine;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> lingua canum tuorum ex inimicis, ab ipso.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Viderunt ingressus tuos, Deus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ingressus Dei mei, regis mei, qui est in sancto.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Pr&aelig;venerunt principes conjuncti psallentibus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in medio juvencularum tympanistriarum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067027vul">27</span>&nbsp;In ecclesiis benedicite Deo Domino de fontibus Isra&euml;l.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Ibi Benjamin adolescentulus, in mentis excessu;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> principes Juda, duces eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> principes Zabulon, principes Nephthali.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Manda, Deus, virtuti tu&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> confirma hoc, Deus, quod operatus es in nobis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067030vul">30</span>&nbsp;A templo tuo in Jerusalem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tibi offerent reges munera.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Increpa feras arundinis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> congregatio taurorum in vaccis populorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut excludant eos qui probati sunt argento.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dissipa gentes qu&aelig; bella volunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Venient legati ex &AElig;gypto;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> &AElig;thiopia pr&aelig;veniet manus ejus Deo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Regna terr&aelig;, cantate Deo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> psallite Domino; psallite Deo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Qui ascendit super c&aelig;lum c&aelig;li, ad orientem:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ecce dabit voci su&aelig; vocem virtutis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Date gloriam Deo super Isra&euml;l;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> magnificentia ejus et virtus ejus in nubibus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa067036vul">36</span>&nbsp;Mirabilis Deus in sanctis suis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Deus Isra&euml;l ipse dabit virtutem et fortitudinem plebi su&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Benedictus Deus!</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
