<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa071001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Psalmus, in Salomonem.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa071002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Deus, judicium tuum regi da,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et justitiam tuam filio regis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> judicare populum tuum in justitia,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et pauperes tuos in judicio.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Suscipiant montes pacem populo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et colles justitiam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Judicabit pauperes populi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et salvos faciet filios pauperum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et humiliabit calumniatorem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Et permanebit cum sole, et ante lunam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in generatione et generationem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Descendet sicut pluvia in vellus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sicut stillicidia stillantia super terram.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Orietur in diebus ejus justitia, et abundantia pacis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> donec auferatur luna.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Et dominabitur a mari usque ad mare,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et a flumine usque ad terminos orbis terrarum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Coram illo procident &AElig;thiopes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inimici ejus terram lingent.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Reges Tharsis et insul&aelig; munera offerent;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> reges Arabum et Saba dona adducent:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071011vul">11</span>&nbsp;et adorabunt eum omnes reges terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> omnes gentes servient ei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Quia liberabit pauperem a potente,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et pauperem cui non erat adjutor.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Parcet pauperi et inopi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et animas pauperum salvas faciet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Ex usuris et iniquitate redimet animas eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et honorabile nomen eorum coram illo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Et vivet, et dabitur ei de auro Arabi&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et adorabunt de ipso semper,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tota die benedicent ei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Et erit firmamentum in terra in summis montium;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> superextolletur super Libanum fructus ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et florebunt de civitate sicut f&oelig;num terr&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Sit nomen ejus benedictum in s&aelig;cula;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ante solem permanet nomen ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et benedicentur in ipso omnes tribus terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> omnes gentes magnificabunt eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Benedictus Dominus Deus Isra&euml;l,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui facit mirabilia solus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa071019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Et benedictum nomen majestatis ejus in &aelig;ternum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et replebitur majestate ejus omnis terra. Fiat, fiat.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro001"><span class="verse" id="psa071020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Defecerunt laudes David, filii Jesse.</span><!--/propar--></p>
