<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa073001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Intellectus Asaph.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Ut quid, Deus, repulisti in finem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> iratus est furor tuus super oves pascu&aelig; tu&aelig;?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Memor esto congregationis tu&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quam possedisti ab initio.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Redemisti virgam h&aelig;reditatis tu&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> mons Sion, in quo habitasti in eo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Leva manus tuas in superbias eorum in finem:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quanta malignatus est inimicus in sancto!</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Et gloriati sunt qui oderunt te in medio solemnitatis tu&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> posuerunt signa sua, signa:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073005vul">5</span>&nbsp;et non cognoverunt sicut in exitu super summum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Quasi in silva lignorum securibus</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073006vul">6</span>&nbsp;exciderunt januas ejus in idipsum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in securi et ascia dejecerunt eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Incenderunt igni sanctuarium tuum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in terra polluerunt tabernaculum nominis tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Dixerunt in corde suo cognatio eorum simul:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Quiescere faciamus omnes dies festos Dei a terra.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Signa nostra non vidimus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> jam non est propheta;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et nos non cognoscet amplius.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Usquequo, Deus, improperabit inimicus?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> irritat adversarius nomen tuum in finem?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Ut quid avertis manum tuam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dexteram tuam de medio sinu tuo in finem?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Deus autem rex noster ante s&aelig;cula:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> operatus est salutem in medio terr&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Tu confirmasti in virtute tua mare;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> contribulasti capita draconum in aquis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Tu confregisti capita draconis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> dedisti eum escam populis &AElig;thiopum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Tu dirupisti fontes et torrentes;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tu siccasti fluvios Ethan.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Tuus est dies, et tua est nox;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tu fabricatus es auroram et solem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Tu fecisti omnes terminos terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> &aelig;statem et ver tu plasmasti ea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Memor esto hujus: inimicus improperavit Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et populus insipiens incitavit nomen tuum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Ne tradas bestiis animas confitentes tibi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et animas pauperum tuorum ne obliviscaris in finem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Respice in testamentum tuum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia repleti sunt qui obscurati sunt terr&aelig; domibus iniquitatum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Ne avertatur humilis factus confusus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> pauper et inops laudabunt nomen tuum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Exsurge, Deus, judica causam tuam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> memor esto improperiorum tuorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> eorum qu&aelig; ab insipiente sunt tota die.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa073023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Ne obliviscaris voces inimicorum tuorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> superbia eorum qui te oderunt ascendit semper.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
