<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa077001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Intellectus Asaph.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Attendite, popule meus, legem meam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> inclinate aurem vestram in verba oris mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Aperiam in parabolis os meum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> loquar propositiones ab initio.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Quanta audivimus, et cognovimus ea,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et patres nostri narraverunt nobis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Non sunt occultata a filiis eorum in generatione altera,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> narrantes laudes Domini et virtutes ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus qu&aelig; fecit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Et suscitavit testimonium in Jacob,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et legem posuit in Isra&euml;l,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quanta mandavit patribus nostris</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nota facere ea filiis suis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077006vul">6</span>&nbsp;ut cognoscat generatio altera:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> filii qui nascentur et exsurgent,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et narrabunt filiis suis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077007vul">7</span>&nbsp;ut ponant in Deo spem suam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non obliviscantur operum Dei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mandata ejus exquirant:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077008vul">8</span>&nbsp;ne fiant, sicut patres eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> generatio prava et exasperans;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> generatio qu&aelig; non direxit cor suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non est creditus cum Deo spiritus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Filii Ephrem, intendentes et mittentes arcum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> conversi sunt in die belli.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Non custodierunt testamentum Dei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in lege ejus noluerunt ambulare.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Et obliti sunt benefactorum ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilium ejus qu&aelig; ostendit eis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Coram patribus eorum fecit mirabilia</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in terra &AElig;gypti, in campo Taneos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Interrupit mare, et perduxit eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et statuit aquas quasi in utre:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077014vul">14</span>&nbsp;et deduxit eos in nube diei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tota nocte in illuminatione ignis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Interrupit petram in eremo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et adaquavit eos velut in abysso multa.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Et eduxit aquam de petra,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et deduxit tamquam flumina aquas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Et apposuerunt adhuc peccare ei;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in iram excitaverunt Excelsum in inaquoso.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Et tentaverunt Deum in cordibus suis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut peterent escas animabus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Et male locuti sunt de Deo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> dixerunt: Numquid poterit Deus parare mensam in deserto?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077020vul">20</span>&nbsp;quoniam percussit petram, et fluxerunt aqu&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et torrentes inundaverunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Numquid et panem poterit dare,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> aut parare mensam populo suo?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Ideo audivit Dominus et distulit;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ignis accensus est in Jacob,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ira ascendit in Isra&euml;l:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077022vul">22</span>&nbsp;quia non crediderunt in Deo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec speraverunt in salutari ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Et mandavit nubibus desuper,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et januas c&aelig;li aperuit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Et pluit illis manna ad manducandum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et panem c&aelig;li dedit eis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Panem angelorum manducavit homo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cibaria misit eis in abundantia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Transtulit austrum de c&aelig;lo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et induxit in virtute sua africum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Et pluit super eos sicut pulverem carnes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sicut arenam maris volatilia pennata.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Et ceciderunt in medio castrorum eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> circa tabernacula eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Et manducaverunt, et saturati sunt nimis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et desiderium eorum attulit eis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077030vul">30</span>&nbsp;non sunt fraudati a desiderio suo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Adhuc esc&aelig; eorum erant in ore ipsorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077031vul">31</span>&nbsp;et ira Dei ascendit super eos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et occidit pingues eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et electos Isra&euml;l impedivit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077032vul">32</span>&nbsp;In omnibus his peccaverunt adhuc,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non crediderunt in mirabilibus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Et defecerunt in vanitate dies eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et anni eorum cum festinatione.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Cum occideret eos, qu&aelig;rebant eum et revertebantur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et diluculo veniebant ad eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Et rememorati sunt quia Deus adjutor est eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Deus excelsus redemptor eorum est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077036vul">36</span>&nbsp;Et dilexerunt eum in ore suo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et lingua sua mentiti sunt ei;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077037vul">37</span>&nbsp;cor autem eorum non erat rectum cum eo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec fideles habiti sunt in testamento ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077038vul">38</span>&nbsp;Ipse autem est misericors,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et propitius fiet peccatis eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non disperdet eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et abundavit ut averteret iram suam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non accendit omnem iram suam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077039vul">39</span>&nbsp;Et recordatus est quia caro sunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> spiritus vadens et non rediens.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077040vul">40</span>&nbsp;Quoties exacerbaverunt eum in deserto;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in iram concitaverunt eum in inaquoso?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077041vul">41</span>&nbsp;Et conversi sunt, et tentaverunt Deum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sanctum Isra&euml;l exacerbaverunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077042vul">42</span>&nbsp;Non sunt recordati manus ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> die qua redemit eos de manu tribulantis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077043vul">43</span>&nbsp;sicut posuit in &AElig;gypto signa sua,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et prodigia sua in campo Taneos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077044vul">44</span>&nbsp;et convertit in sanguinem flumina eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et imbres eorum, ne biberent.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077045vul">45</span>&nbsp;Misit in eos c&oelig;nomyiam, et comedit eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ranam, et disperdidit eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077046vul">46</span>&nbsp;et dedit &aelig;rugini fructus eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et labores eorum locust&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077047vul">47</span>&nbsp;et occidit in grandine vineas eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et moros eorum in pruina;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077048vul">48</span>&nbsp;et tradidit grandini jumenta eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et possessionem eorum igni;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077049vul">49</span>&nbsp;misit in eos iram indignationis su&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> indignationem, et iram, et tribulationem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> immissiones per angelos malos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077050vul">50</span>&nbsp;Viam fecit semit&aelig; ir&aelig; su&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non pepercit a morte animabus eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et jumenta eorum in morte conclusit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077051vul">51</span>&nbsp;et percussit omne primogenitum in terra &AElig;gypti;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> primitias omnis laboris eorum in tabernaculis Cham:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077052vul">52</span>&nbsp;et abstulit sicut oves populum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et perduxit eos tamquam gregem in deserto:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077053vul">53</span>&nbsp;et deduxit eos in spe, et non timuerunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inimicos eorum operuit mare.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077054vul">54</span>&nbsp;Et induxit eos in montem sanctificationis su&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> montem quem acquisivit dextera ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ejecit a facie eorum gentes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sorte divisit eis terram in funiculo distributionis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077055vul">55</span>&nbsp;et habitare fecit in tabernaculis eorum tribus Isra&euml;l.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077056vul">56</span>&nbsp;Et tentaverunt, et exacerbaverunt Deum excelsum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et testimonia ejus non custodierunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077057vul">57</span>&nbsp;Et averterunt se, et non servaverunt pactum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quemadmodum patres eorum, conversi sunt in arcum pravum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077058vul">58</span>&nbsp;In iram concitaverunt eum in collibus suis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in sculptilibus suis ad &aelig;mulationem eum provocaverunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077059vul">59</span>&nbsp;Audivit Deus, et sprevit,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ad nihilum redegit valde Isra&euml;l.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077060vul">60</span>&nbsp;Et repulit tabernaculum Silo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tabernaculum suum, ubi habitavit in hominibus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077061vul">61</span>&nbsp;Et tradidit in captivitatem virtutem eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et pulchritudinem eorum in manus inimici.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077062vul">62</span>&nbsp;Et conclusit in gladio populum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et h&aelig;reditatem suam sprevit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077063vul">63</span>&nbsp;Juvenes eorum comedit ignis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et virgines eorum non sunt lamentat&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077064vul">64</span>&nbsp;Sacerdotes eorum in gladio ceciderunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et vidu&aelig; eorum non plorabantur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077065vul">65</span>&nbsp;Et excitatus est tamquam dormiens Dominus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tamquam potens crapulatus a vino.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077066vul">66</span>&nbsp;Et percussit inimicos suos in posteriora;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> opprobrium sempiternum dedit illis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077067vul">67</span>&nbsp;Et repulit tabernaculum Joseph,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tribum Ephraim non elegit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077068vul">68</span>&nbsp;sed elegit tribum Juda,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> montem Sion, quem dilexit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077069vul">69</span>&nbsp;Et &aelig;dificavit sicut unicornium sanctificium suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in terra quam fundavit in s&aelig;cula.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077070vul">70</span>&nbsp;Et elegit David, servum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sustulit eum de gregibus ovium;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de post f&oelig;tantes accepit eum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077071vul">71</span>&nbsp;pascere Jacob servum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Isra&euml;l h&aelig;reditatem suam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa077072vul">72</span>&nbsp;Et pavit eos in innocentia cordis sui,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in intellectibus manuum suarum deduxit eos.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
