<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa096001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Huic David, quando terra ejus restituta est.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Dominus regnavit: exsultet terra;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> l&aelig;tentur insul&aelig; mult&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Nubes et caligo in circuitu ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> justitia et judicium correctio sedis ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Ignis ante ipsum pr&aelig;cedet,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inflammabit in circuitu inimicos ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Illuxerunt fulgura ejus orbi terr&aelig;;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vidit, et commota est terra.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Montes sicut cera fluxerunt a facie Domini;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a facie Domini omnis terra.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Annuntiaverunt c&aelig;li justitiam ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et viderunt omnes populi gloriam ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Confundantur omnes qui adorant sculptilia,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qui gloriantur in simulacris suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Adorate eum omnes angeli ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Audivit, et l&aelig;tata est Sion,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exsultaverunt fili&aelig; Jud&aelig;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> propter judicia tua, Domine.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Quoniam tu Dominus altissimus super omnem terram;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nimis exaltatus es super omnes deos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Qui diligitis Dominum, odite malum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> custodit Dominus animas sanctorum suorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de manu peccatoris liberabit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Lux orta est justo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et rectis corde l&aelig;titia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa096012vul">12</span>&nbsp;L&aelig;tamini, justi, in Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et confitemini memori&aelig; sanctificationis ejus.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
