<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa101001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Oratio pauperis, cum anxius fuerit, et in conspectu Domini effuderit precem suam.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa101002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Domine, exaudi orationem meam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et clamor meus ad te veniat.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Non avertas faciem tuam a me:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in quacumque die tribulor, inclina ad me aurem tuam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in quacumque die invocavero te, velociter exaudi me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Quia defecerunt sicut fumus dies mei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ossa mea sicut cremium aruerunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Percussus sum ut f&oelig;num, et aruit cor meum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia oblitus sum comedere panem meum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101006vul">6</span>&nbsp;A voce gemitus mei</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> adh&aelig;sit os meum carni me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Similis factus sum pellicano solitudinis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> factus sum sicut nycticorax in domicilio.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Vigilavi, et factus sum sicut passer solitarius in tecto.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Tota die exprobrabant mihi inimici mei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qui laudabant me adversum me jurabant:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101010vul">10</span>&nbsp;quia cinerem tamquam panem manducabam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et potum meum cum fletu miscebam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101011vul">11</span>&nbsp;a facie ir&aelig; et indignationis tu&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia elevans allisisti me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Dies mei sicut umbra declinaverunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ego sicut f&oelig;num arui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Tu autem, Domine, in &aelig;ternum permanes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et memoriale tuum in generationem et generationem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Tu exsurgens misereberis Sion,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia tempus miserendi ejus, quia venit tempus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101015vul">15</span>&nbsp;quoniam placuerunt servis tuis lapides ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et terr&aelig; ejus miserebuntur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Et timebunt gentes nomen tuum, Domine,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omnes reges terr&aelig; gloriam tuam:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101017vul">17</span>&nbsp;quia &aelig;dificavit Dominus Sion,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et videbitur in gloria sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Respexit in orationem humilium</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non sprevit precem eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Scribantur h&aelig;c in generatione altera,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et populus qui creabitur laudabit Dominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Quia prospexit de excelso sancto suo;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dominus de c&aelig;lo in terram aspexit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101021vul">21</span>&nbsp;ut audiret gemitus compeditorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut solveret filios interemptorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101022vul">22</span>&nbsp;ut annuntient in Sion nomen Domini,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et laudem ejus in Jerusalem:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101023vul">23</span>&nbsp;in conveniendo populos in unum, et reges,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut serviant Domino.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Respondit ei in via virtutis su&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Paucitatem dierum meorum nuntia mihi:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101025vul">25</span>&nbsp;ne revoces me in dimidio dierum meorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in generationem et generationem anni tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Initio tu, Domine, terram fundasti,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et opera manuum tuarum sunt c&aelig;li.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Ipsi peribunt, tu autem permanes;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omnes sicut vestimentum veterascent.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et sicut opertorium mutabis eos, et mutabuntur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101028vul">28</span>&nbsp;tu autem idem ipse es, et anni tui non deficient.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa101029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Filii servorum tuorum habitabunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et semen eorum in s&aelig;culum dirigetur.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
