<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa102001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Benedic, anima mea, Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omnia qu&aelig; intra me sunt nomini sancto ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Benedic, anima mea, Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et noli oblivisci omnes retributiones ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Qui propitiatur omnibus iniquitatibus tuis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui sanat omnes infirmitates tuas:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102004vul">4</span>&nbsp;qui redimit de interitu vitam tuam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui coronat te in misericordia et miserationibus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102005vul">5</span>&nbsp;qui replet in bonis desiderium tuum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> renovabitur ut aquil&aelig; juventus tua:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102006vul">6</span>&nbsp;faciens misericordias Dominus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et judicium omnibus injuriam patientibus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Notas fecit vias suas Moysi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> filiis Isra&euml;l voluntates suas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Miserator et misericors Dominus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> longanimis, et multum misericors.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Non in perpetuum irascetur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> neque in &aelig;ternum comminabitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Non secundum peccata nostra fecit nobis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> neque secundum iniquitates nostras retribuit nobis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Quoniam secundum altitudinem c&aelig;li a terra,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> corroboravit misericordiam suam super timentes se;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102012vul">12</span>&nbsp;quantum distat ortus ab occidente,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> longe fecit a nobis iniquitates nostras.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Quomodo miseretur pater filiorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> misertus est Dominus timentibus se.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Quoniam ipse cognovit figmentum nostrum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> recordatus est quoniam pulvis sumus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Homo, sicut f&oelig;num dies ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> tamquam flos agri, sic efflorebit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102016vul">16</span>&nbsp;quoniam spiritus pertransibit in illo, et non subsistet,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non cognoscet amplius locum suum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Misericordia autem Domini ab &aelig;terno,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et usque in &aelig;ternum super timentes eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et justitia illius in filios filiorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102018vul">18</span>&nbsp;his qui servant testamentum ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et memores sunt mandatorum ipsius ad faciendum ea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Dominus in c&aelig;lo paravit sedem suam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et regnum ipsius omnibus dominabitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Benedicite Domino, omnes angeli ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> potentes virtute, facientes verbum illius,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ad audiendam vocem sermonum ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Benedicite Domino, omnes virtutes ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ministri ejus, qui facitis voluntatem ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa102022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Benedicite Domino, omnia opera ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in omni loco dominationis ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> benedic, anima mea, Domino.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
