<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa103001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Benedic, anima mea, Domino:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Domine Deus meus, magnificatus es vehementer.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Confessionem et decorem induisti,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103002vul">2</span>&nbsp;amictus lumine sicut vestimento.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Extendens c&aelig;lum sicut pellem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103003vul">3</span>&nbsp;qui tegis aquis superiora ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui ponis nubem ascensum tuum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui ambulas super pennas ventorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103004vul">4</span>&nbsp;qui facis angelos tuos spiritus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ministros tuos ignem urentem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Qui fundasti terram super stabilitatem suam:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non inclinabitur in s&aelig;culum s&aelig;culi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Abyssus sicut vestimentum amictus ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> super montes stabunt aqu&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Ab increpatione tua fugient;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a voce tonitrui tui formidabunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Ascendunt montes, et descendunt campi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in locum quem fundasti eis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Terminum posuisti quem non transgredientur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> neque convertentur operire terram.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Qui emittis fontes in convallibus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> inter medium montium pertransibunt aqu&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Potabunt omnes besti&aelig; agri;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> expectabunt onagri in siti sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Super ea volucres c&aelig;li habitabunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de medio petrarum dabunt voces.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Rigans montes de superioribus suis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> de fructu operum tuorum satiabitur terra:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103014vul">14</span>&nbsp;producens f&oelig;num jumentis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et herbam servituti hominum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut educas panem de terra,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103015vul">15</span>&nbsp;et vinum l&aelig;tificet cor hominis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut exhilaret faciem in oleo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et panis cor hominis confirmet.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Saturabuntur ligna campi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cedri Libani quas plantavit:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103017vul">17</span>&nbsp;illic passeres nidificabunt:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> herodii domus dux est eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Montes excelsi cervis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> petra refugium herinaciis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Fecit lunam in tempora;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sol cognovit occasum suum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Posuisti tenebras, et facta est nox;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in ipsa pertransibunt omnes besti&aelig; silv&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103021vul">21</span>&nbsp;catuli leonum rugientes ut rapiant,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qu&aelig;rant a Deo escam sibi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Ortus est sol, et congregati sunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in cubilibus suis collocabuntur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Exibit homo ad opus suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ad operationem suam usque ad vesperum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Quam magnificata sunt opera tua, Domine!</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> omnia in sapientia fecisti;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> impleta est terra possessione tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Hoc mare magnum et spatiosum manibus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> illic reptilia quorum non est numerus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> animalia pusilla cum magnis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Illic naves pertransibunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> draco iste quem formasti ad illudendum ei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Omnia a te expectant</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut des illis escam in tempore.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Dante te illis, colligent;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> aperiente te manum tuam, omnia implebuntur bonitate.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Avertente autem te faciem, turbabuntur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> auferes spiritum eorum, et deficient,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in pulverem suum revertentur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Emittes spiritum tuum, et creabuntur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et renovabis faciem terr&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Sit gloria Domini in s&aelig;culum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> l&aelig;tabitur Dominus in operibus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Qui respicit terram, et facit eam tremere;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui tangit montes, et fumigant.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Cantabo Domino in vita mea;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> psallam Deo meo quamdiu sum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Jucundum sit ei eloquium meum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ego vero delectabor in Domino.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa103035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Deficiant peccatores a terra,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et iniqui, ita ut non sint.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Benedic, anima mea, Domino.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
