<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa104001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Alleluja.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Confitemini Domino, et invocate nomen ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> annuntiate inter gentes opera ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Cantate ei, et psallite ei;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> narrate omnia mirabilia ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Laudamini in nomine sancto ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> l&aelig;tetur cor qu&aelig;rentium Dominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Qu&aelig;rite Dominum, et confirmamini;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qu&aelig;rite faciem ejus semper.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Mementote mirabilium ejus qu&aelig; fecit;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> prodigia ejus, et judicia oris ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104006vul">6</span>&nbsp;semen Abraham servi ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> filii Jacob electi ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Ipse Dominus Deus noster;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in universa terra judicia ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Memor fuit in s&aelig;culum testamenti sui;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> verbi quod mandavit in mille generationes:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104009vul">9</span>&nbsp;quod disposuit ad Abraham,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et juramenti sui ad Isaac:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104010vul">10</span>&nbsp;et statuit illud Jacob in pr&aelig;ceptum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Isra&euml;l in testamentum &aelig;ternum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104011vul">11</span>&nbsp;dicens: Tibi dabo terram Chanaan,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> funiculum h&aelig;reditatis vestr&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104012vul">12</span>&nbsp;cum essent numero brevi,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> paucissimi, et incol&aelig; ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Et pertransierunt de gente in gentem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de regno ad populum alterum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Non reliquit hominem nocere eis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et corripuit pro eis reges.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Nolite tangere christos meos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in prophetis meis nolite malignari.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Et vocavit famem super terram,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omne firmamentum panis contrivit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Misit ante eos virum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in servum venundatus est, Joseph.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Humiliaverunt in compedibus pedes ejus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ferrum pertransiit animam ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104019vul">19</span>&nbsp;donec veniret verbum ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Eloquium Domini inflammavit eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Misit rex, et solvit eum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> princeps populorum, et dimisit eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Constituit eum dominum domus su&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et principem omnis possessionis su&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104022vul">22</span>&nbsp;ut erudiret principes ejus sicut semetipsum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et senes ejus prudentiam doceret.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Et intravit Isra&euml;l in &AElig;gyptum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Jacob accola fuit in terra Cham.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Et auxit populum suum vehementer,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et firmavit eum super inimicos ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Convertit cor eorum, ut odirent populum ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dolum facerent in servos ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Misit Moysen servum suum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Aaron quem elegit ipsum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Posuit in eis verba signorum suorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et prodigiorum in terra Cham.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Misit tenebras, et obscuravit;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non exacerbavit sermones suos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Convertit aquas eorum in sanguinem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et occidit pisces eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Edidit terra eorum ranas</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in penetralibus regum ipsorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Dixit, et venit c&oelig;nomyia et ciniphes</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in omnibus finibus eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Posuit pluvias eorum grandinem:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ignem comburentem in terra ipsorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Et percussit vineas eorum, et ficulneas eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et contrivit lignum finium eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Dixit, et venit locusta,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et bruchus cujus non erat numerus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104035vul">35</span>&nbsp;et comedit omne f&oelig;num in terra eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et comedit omnem fructum terr&aelig; eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104036vul">36</span>&nbsp;Et percussit omne primogenitum in terra eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> primitias omnis laboris eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104037vul">37</span>&nbsp;Et eduxit eos cum argento et auro,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non erat in tribubus eorum infirmus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104038vul">38</span>&nbsp;L&aelig;tata est &AElig;gyptus in profectione eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia incubuit timor eorum super eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104039vul">39</span>&nbsp;Expandit nubem in protectionem eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ignem ut luceret eis per noctem.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104040vul">40</span>&nbsp;Petierunt, et venit coturnix,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et pane c&aelig;li saturavit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104041vul">41</span>&nbsp;Dirupit petram, et fluxerunt aqu&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> abierunt in sicco flumina.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104042vul">42</span>&nbsp;Quoniam memor fuit verbi sancti sui,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quod habuit ad Abraham puerum suum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104043vul">43</span>&nbsp;Et eduxit populum suum in exsultatione,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et electos suos in l&aelig;titia.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104044vul">44</span>&nbsp;Et dedit illis regiones gentium,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et labores populorum possederunt:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa104045vul">45</span>&nbsp;ut custodiant justificationes ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et legem ejus requirant.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
