<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa105001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Alleluja.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Confitemini Domino, quoniam bonus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam in s&aelig;culum misericordia ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Quis loquetur potentias Domini;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> auditas faciet omnes laudes ejus?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Beati qui custodiunt judicium,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et faciunt justitiam in omni tempore.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Memento nostri, Domine, in beneplacito populi tui;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> visita nos in salutari tuo:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105005vul">5</span>&nbsp;ad videndum in bonitate electorum tuorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ad l&aelig;tandum in l&aelig;titia gentis tu&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut lauderis cum h&aelig;reditate tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Peccavimus cum patribus nostris:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> injuste egimus; iniquitatem fecimus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Patres nostri in &AElig;gypto non intellexerunt mirabilia tua;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non fuerunt memores multitudinis misericordi&aelig; tu&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et irritaverunt ascendentes in mare, mare Rubrum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105008vul">8</span>&nbsp;et salvavit eos propter nomen suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut notam faceret potentiam suam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Et increpuit mare Rubrum et exsiccatum est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et deduxit eos in abyssis sicut in deserto.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Et salvavit eos de manu odientium,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et redemit eos de manu inimici.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Et operuit aqua tribulantes eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> unus ex eis non remansit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Et crediderunt verbis ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et laudaverunt laudem ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Cito fecerunt; obliti sunt operum ejus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non sustinuerunt consilium ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Et concupierunt concupiscentiam in deserto,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tentaverunt Deum in inaquoso.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Et dedit eis petitionem ipsorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et misit saturitatem in animas eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Et irritaverunt Moysen in castris;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Aaron, sanctum Domini.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Aperta est terra, et deglutivit Dathan,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et operuit super congregationem Abiron.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Et exarsit ignis in synagoga eorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> flamma combussit peccatores.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Et fecerunt vitulum in Horeb,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et adoraverunt sculptile.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Et mutaverunt gloriam suam</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in similitudinem vituli comedentis f&oelig;num.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Obliti sunt Deum qui salvavit eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui fecit magnalia in &AElig;gypto,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105022vul">22</span>&nbsp;mirabilia in terra Cham,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> terribilia in mari Rubro.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Et dixit ut disperderet eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> si non Moyses, electus ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> stetisset in confractione in conspectu ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut averteret iram ejus, ne disperderet eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Et pro nihilo habuerunt terram desiderabilem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non crediderunt verbo ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Et murmuraverunt in tabernaculis suis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> non exaudierunt vocem Domini.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Et elevavit manum suam super eos</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut prosterneret eos in deserto:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105027vul">27</span>&nbsp;et ut dejiceret semen eorum in nationibus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dispergeret eos in regionibus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Et initiati sunt Beelphegor,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et comederunt sacrificia mortuorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Et irritaverunt eum in adinventionibus suis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et multiplicata est in eis ruina.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Et stetit Phinees, et placavit,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cessavit quassatio.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Et reputatum est ei in justitiam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in generationem et generationem usque in sempiternum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Et irritaverunt eum ad aquas contradictionis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et vexatus est Moyses propter eos:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105033vul">33</span>&nbsp;quia exacerbaverunt spiritum ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et distinxit in labiis suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105034vul">34</span>&nbsp;Non disperdiderunt gentes</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quas dixit Dominus illis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105035vul">35</span>&nbsp;et commisti sunt inter gentes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et didicerunt opera eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105036vul">36</span>&nbsp;et servierunt sculptilibus eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et factum est illis in scandalum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105037vul">37</span>&nbsp;Et immolaverunt filios suos et filias suas d&aelig;moniis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105038vul">38</span>&nbsp;Et effuderunt sanguinem innocentem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sanguinem filiorum suorum et filiarum suarum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quas sacrificaverunt sculptilibus Chanaan.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et infecta est terra in sanguinibus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105039vul">39</span>&nbsp;et contaminata est in operibus eorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et fornicati sunt in adinventionibus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105040vul">40</span>&nbsp;Et iratus est furore Dominus in populum suum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et abominatus est h&aelig;reditatem suam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105041vul">41</span>&nbsp;Et tradidit eos in manus gentium;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dominati sunt eorum qui oderunt eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105042vul">42</span>&nbsp;Et tribulaverunt eos inimici eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et humiliati sunt sub manibus eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105043vul">43</span>&nbsp;s&aelig;pe liberavit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Ipsi autem exacerbaverunt eum in consilio suo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et humiliati sunt in iniquitatibus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105044vul">44</span>&nbsp;Et vidit cum tribularentur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et audivit orationem eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105045vul">45</span>&nbsp;Et memor fuit testamenti sui,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et p&oelig;nituit eum secundum multitudinem misericordi&aelig; su&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105046vul">46</span>&nbsp;et dedit eos in misericordias,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in conspectu omnium qui ceperant eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105047vul">47</span>&nbsp;Salvos nos fac, Domine Deus noster,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et congrega nos de nationibus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut confiteamur nomini sancto tuo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et gloriemur in laude tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa105048vul">48</span>&nbsp;Benedictus Dominus Deus Isra&euml;l, a s&aelig;culo et usque in s&aelig;culum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dicet omnis populus: Fiat, fiat.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
