<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa106001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Alleluja.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Confitemini Domino, quoniam bonus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quoniam in s&aelig;culum misericordia ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Dicant qui redempti sunt a Domino,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quos redemit de manu inimici,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de regionibus congregavit eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106003vul">3</span>&nbsp;a solis ortu, et occasu, ab aquilone, et mari.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Erraverunt in solitudine, in inaquoso;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> viam civitatis habitaculi non invenerunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Esurientes et sitientes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> anima eorum in ipsis defecit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Et clamaverunt ad Dominum cum tribularentur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de necessitatibus eorum eripuit eos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106007vul">7</span>&nbsp;et deduxit eos in viam rectam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut irent in civitatem habitationis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Confiteantur Domino misericordi&aelig; ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus filiis hominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Quia satiavit animam inanem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et animam esurientem satiavit bonis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Sedentes in tenebris et umbra mortis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> vinctos in mendicitate et ferro.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Quia exacerbaverunt eloquia Dei,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et consilium Altissimi irritaverunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Et humiliatum est in laboribus cor eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> infirmati sunt, nec fuit qui adjuvaret.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Et clamaverunt ad Dominum cum tribularentur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de necessitatibus eorum liberavit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Et eduxit eos de tenebris et umbra mortis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et vincula eorum dirupit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Confiteantur Domino misericordi&aelig; ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus filiis hominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Quia contrivit portas &aelig;reas,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et vectes ferreos confregit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Suscepit eos de via iniquitatis eorum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> propter injustitias enim suas humiliati sunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Omnem escam abominata est anima eorum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et appropinquaverunt usque ad portas mortis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Et clamaverunt ad Dominum cum tribularentur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de necessitatibus eorum liberavit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Misit verbum suum, et sanavit eos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et eripuit eos de interitionibus eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Confiteantur Domino misericordi&aelig; ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus filiis hominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Et sacrificent sacrificium laudis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et annuntient opera ejus in exsultatione.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Qui descendunt mare in navibus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> facientes operationem in aquis multis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106024vul">24</span>&nbsp;ipsi viderunt opera Domini,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus in profundo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Dixit, et stetit spiritus procell&aelig;,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exaltati sunt fluctus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Ascendunt usque ad c&aelig;los, et descendunt usque ad abyssos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> anima eorum in malis tabescebat.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Turbati sunt, et moti sunt sicut ebrius,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omnis sapientia eorum devorata est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Et clamaverunt ad Dominum cum tribularentur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et de necessitatibus eorum eduxit eos.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Et statuit procellam ejus in auram,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et siluerunt fluctus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Et l&aelig;tati sunt quia siluerunt;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et deduxit eos in portum voluntatis eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106031vul">31</span>&nbsp;Confiteantur Domino misericordi&aelig; ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et mirabilia ejus filiis hominum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106032vul">32</span>&nbsp;Et exaltent eum in ecclesia plebis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in cathedra seniorum laudent eum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106033vul">33</span>&nbsp;Posuit flumina in desertum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et exitus aquarum in sitim;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106034vul">34</span>&nbsp;terram fructiferam in salsuginem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a malitia inhabitantium in ea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106035vul">35</span>&nbsp;Posuit desertum in stagna aquarum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et terram sine aqua in exitus aquarum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106036vul">36</span>&nbsp;Et collocavit illic esurientes,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et constituerunt civitatem habitationis:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106037vul">37</span>&nbsp;et seminaverunt agros et plantaverunt vineas,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et fecerunt fructum nativitatis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106038vul">38</span>&nbsp;Et benedixit eis, et multiplicati sunt nimis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et jumenta eorum non minoravit.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106039vul">39</span>&nbsp;Et pauci facti sunt et vexati sunt,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> a tribulatione malorum et dolore.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106040vul">40</span>&nbsp;Effusa est contemptio super principes:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et errare fecit eos in invio, et non in via.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106041vul">41</span>&nbsp;Et adjuvit pauperem de inopia,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et posuit sicut oves familias.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106042vul">42</span>&nbsp;Videbunt recti, et l&aelig;tabuntur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et omnis iniquitas oppilabit os suum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa106043vul">43</span>&nbsp;Quis sapiens, et custodiet h&aelig;c,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et intelliget misericordias Domini?</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
