<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa107001vul">1</span>&nbsp;Canticum Psalmi, ipsi David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa107002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Paratum cor meum, Deus, paratum cor meum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> cantabo, et psallam in gloria mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Exsurge, gloria mea; exsurge, psalterium et cithara;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> exsurgam diluculo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Confitebor tibi in populis, Domine,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et psallam tibi in nationibus:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107005vul">5</span>&nbsp;quia magna est super c&aelig;los misericordia tua,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et usque ad nubes veritas tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Exaltare super c&aelig;los, Deus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et super omnem terram gloria tua:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107007vul">7</span>&nbsp;ut liberentur dilecti tui.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Salvum fac dextera tua, et exaudi me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Deus locutus est in sancto suo:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Exsultabo, et dividam Sichimam;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et convallem tabernaculorum dimetiar.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Meus est Galaad, et meus est Manasses,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et Ephraim susceptio capitis mei.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Juda rex meus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Moab lebes spei me&aelig;:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in Idum&aelig;am extendam calceamentum meum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> mihi alienigen&aelig; amici facti sunt.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Quis deducet me in civitatem munitam?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quis deducet me usque in Idum&aelig;am?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107012vul">12</span>&nbsp;nonne tu, Deus, qui repulisti nos?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et non exibis, Deus, in virtutibus nostris?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Da nobis auxilium de tribulatione,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia vana salus hominis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa107014vul">14</span>&nbsp;In Deo faciemus virtutem;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ipse ad nihilum deducet inimicos nostros.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
