<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa108001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem. Psalmus David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001"><span class="verse" id="psa108002vul">2</span>&nbsp;Deus, laudem meam ne tacueris,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia os peccatoris et os dolosi super me apertum est.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Locuti sunt adversum me lingua dolosa,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sermonibus odii circumdederunt me:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et expugnaverunt me gratis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108004vul">4</span>&nbsp;Pro eo ut me diligerent, detrahebant mihi;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ego autem orabam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Et posuerunt adversum me mala pro bonis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et odium pro dilectione mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Constitue super eum peccatorem,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et diabolus stet a dextris ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Cum judicatur, exeat condemnatus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et oratio ejus fiat in peccatum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Fiant dies ejus pauci,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et episcopatum ejus accipiat alter.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Fiant filii ejus orphani,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et uxor ejus vidua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108010vul">10</span>&nbsp;Nutantes transferantur filii ejus et mendicent,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et ejiciantur de habitationibus suis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Scrutetur f&oelig;nerator omnem substantiam ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et diripiant alieni labores ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Non sit illi adjutor,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nec sit qui misereatur pupillis ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Fiant nati ejus in interitum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> in generatione una deleatur nomen ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108014vul">14</span>&nbsp;In memoriam redeat iniquitas patrum ejus in conspectu Domini,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et peccatum matris ejus non deleatur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Fiant contra Dominum semper,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et dispereat de terra memoria eorum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108016vul">16</span>&nbsp;pro eo quod non est recordatus facere misericordiam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108017vul">17</span>&nbsp;et persecutus est hominem inopem et mendicum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et compunctum corde, mortificare.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Et dilexit maledictionem, et veniet ei;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et noluit benedictionem, et elongabitur ab eo.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Et induit maledictionem sicut vestimentum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et intravit sicut aqua in interiora ejus,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sicut oleum in ossibus ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Fiat ei sicut vestimentum quo operitur,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et sicut zona qua semper pr&aelig;cingitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108020vul">20</span>&nbsp;Hoc opus eorum qui detrahunt mihi apud Dominum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et qui loquuntur mala adversus animam meam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Et tu, Domine, Domine, fac mecum propter nomen tuum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia suavis est misericordia tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Libera me, quia egenus et pauper ego sum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et cor meum conturbatum est intra me.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Sicut umbra cum declinat ablatus sum,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et excussus sum sicut locust&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Genua mea infirmata sunt a jejunio,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et caro mea immutata est propter oleum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108025vul">25</span>&nbsp;Et ego factus sum opprobrium illis;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> viderunt me, et moverunt capita sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108026vul">26</span>&nbsp;Adjuva me, Domine Deus meus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> salvum me fac secundum misericordiam tuam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108027vul">27</span>&nbsp;Et sciant quia manus tua h&aelig;c,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tu, Domine, fecisti eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108028vul">28</span>&nbsp;Maledicent illi, et tu benedices:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> qui insurgunt in me confundantur;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> servus autem tuus l&aelig;tabitur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108029vul">29</span>&nbsp;Induantur qui detrahunt mihi pudore,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et operiantur sicut diploide confusione sua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108030vul">30</span>&nbsp;Confitebor Domino nimis in ore meo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in medio multorum laudabo eum:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa108031vul">31</span>&nbsp;quia astitit a dextris pauperis,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> ut salvam faceret a persequentibus animam meam.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
