<h2>Latin (Clementine Vulgate)</h2>
<!--propar--><p class="bibleprose"><span class="pro000"><span class="verse" id="psa138001vul">1</span>&nbsp;In finem, psalmus David.</span><!--/propar--></p>
<!--poepar--><blockquote class="biblepoem"><span class="poe001">Domine, probasti me, et cognovisti me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138002vul">2</span>&nbsp;tu cognovisti sessionem meam et resurrectionem meam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138003vul">3</span>&nbsp;Intellexisti cogitationes meas de longe;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> semitam meam et funiculum meum investigasti:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138004vul">4</span>&nbsp;et omnes vias meas pr&aelig;vidisti,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> quia non est sermo in lingua mea.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138005vul">5</span>&nbsp;Ecce, Domine, tu cognovisti omnia,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> novissima et antiqua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Tu formasti me, et posuisti super me manum tuam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138006vul">6</span>&nbsp;Mirabilis facta est scientia tua ex me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> confortata est, et non potero ad eam.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138007vul">7</span>&nbsp;Quo ibo a spiritu tuo?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et quo a facie tua fugiam?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138008vul">8</span>&nbsp;Si ascendero in c&aelig;lum, tu illic es;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> si descendero in infernum, ades.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138009vul">9</span>&nbsp;Si sumpsero pennas meas diluculo,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et habitavero in extremis maris,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138010vul">10</span>&nbsp;etenim illuc manus tua deducet me,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et tenebit me dextera tua.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138011vul">11</span>&nbsp;Et dixi: Forsitan tenebr&aelig; conculcabunt me;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et nox illuminatio mea in deliciis meis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138012vul">12</span>&nbsp;Quia tenebr&aelig; non obscurabuntur a te,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et nox sicut dies illuminabitur:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> sicut tenebr&aelig; ejus, ita et lumen ejus.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138013vul">13</span>&nbsp;Quia tu possedisti renes meos;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> suscepisti me de utero matris me&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138014vul">14</span>&nbsp;Confitebor tibi, quia terribiliter magnificatus es;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> mirabilia opera tua, et anima mea cognoscit nimis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138015vul">15</span>&nbsp;Non est occultatum os meum a te, quod fecisti in occulto;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et substantia mea in inferioribus terr&aelig;.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138016vul">16</span>&nbsp;Imperfectum meum viderunt oculi tui,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et in libro tuo omnes scribentur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Dies formabuntur, et nemo in eis.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138017vul">17</span>&nbsp;Mihi autem nimis honorificati sunt amici tui, Deus;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> nimis confortatus est principatus eorum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138018vul">18</span>&nbsp;Dinumerabo eos, et super arenam multiplicabuntur.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Exsurrexi, et adhuc sum tecum.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138019vul">19</span>&nbsp;Si occideris, Deus, peccatores,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> viri sanguinum, declinate a me:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138020vul">20</span>&nbsp;quia dicitis in cogitatione:</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> Accipient in vanitate civitates tuas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138021vul">21</span>&nbsp;Nonne qui oderunt te, Domine, oderam,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et super inimicos tuos tabescebam?</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138022vul">22</span>&nbsp;Perfecto odio oderam illos,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et inimici facti sunt mihi.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138023vul">23</span>&nbsp;Proba me, Deus, et scito cor meum;</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> interroga me, et cognosce semitas meas.</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"><span class="verse" id="psa138024vul">24</span>&nbsp;Et vide si via iniquitatis in me est,</span><!--poebre--><br />
<span class="poe002"> et deduc me in via &aelig;terna.</span><!--poepar--></blockquote>
